9:08 AM Prosecuting attorney Yolanda J. Tienstra in court for the State of Wisconsin.  Defendant Nathan James Ward in court. Defendant wishes to accept offer. Court reviews right to counsel. Defendant waives counsel. victim rights compliance. Court accepts waiver of counsel; reviews rights, charges and penalties. Defendant enters NC plea. Court accepts plea and finds guilty. ADA Tienstra heard. Defendant waives statement. Court heard and imposes sentence:

1 yr probation w/h;
AODA & follow through;
Absolute Sobriety;
No bars/taverns/liquor stores etc;
DNA sample & surcharge;
Court costs;
